<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="Indimi_Wikipediya_ibonekamo">Indimi Wikipediya ibonekamo</h2></div>
<div id="lang">
<p>Iyi Wikipediya yanditswe mu <a href="/wiki/Rurimi_rw%27Ikinyarwanda" title="Rurimi rw'Ikinyarwanda">Kinyarwanda</a>. Kuva yatangira mu 2001, ifite kugeza ubu inyandiko zigera kuri <a href="/wiki/Ibidasanzwe:Statistics" title="Ibidasanzwe:Statistics">8.590</a> articles. Hariho izindi Wikipediya mu zindi ndimi nyinshi; zimwe muri zo zigaragaraho kuba nini cyane zagaragajwe hasi aha.
</p>

    Indimi Wikipediya ibonekamo

    Iyi Wikipediya yanditswe mu Kinyarwanda. Kuva yatangira mu 2001, ifite kugeza ubu inyandiko zigera kuri 8.590 articles. Hariho izindi Wikipediya mu zindi ndimi nyinshi; zimwe muri zo zigaragaraho kuba nini cyane zagaragajwe hasi aha.

    • Hejuru y'inyandiko 50,000: BahasaIndonesia Dansk Eesti Lietuvi Slovenina / Srpski Ting Vit

Imishinga ifitanye isano na Wikipediya

Wikipediya icungwa na Fondasiyo ya Wikimediya , umuryango udaharanira inyungu ari na wo unacunga indi mishinga myinshi ya wikimediya:[1]

Commons
Ahashyirwa ibintu amashusho,amafoto ndetse n'amajwi rusange by'ubuntu 		Wikinews
Amakuru y'ubuntu 		Wiktionary
Inkoranya n'Inkoranyanzimbuzi
Wikiquote
Ikoranyirizo ry'amagambo yavuzwe cyangwa yanditswe afite ubusobanuro . 		Wikibooks
Ibitabo n'izindi nyandiko z'ubuntu 		Wikisource
Isomero ry'ibitabo ku buntu
Wikispecies
Ikusanirizo ry'ubwoko bwose bw'ibinyabuzima 		Wikiversity
Imfashanyigisho z'ubuntu 		Meta-Wiki
Ihuzabikorwa by'umushinga wa Wikimediya

Indimi Wikipediya ibonekamo

Iyi Wikipediya yanditswe mu Kinyarwanda. Kuva yatangira mu 2001, ifite kugeza ubu inyandiko zigera kuri 8.590 articles. Hariho izindi Wikipediya mu zindi ndimi nyinshi; zimwe muri zo zigaragaraho kuba nini cyane zagaragajwe hasi aha.

  • Hejuru y'inyandiko 7,053,667:English Deutsch Espaol Franais Italiano Nederlands Polski Portugus
  • Hejuru y'inyandiko 100,000: Catal etina Esperanto Magyar Norsk (bokml) Romn Slovenina Suomi Svenska Trke
  • Hejuru y'inyandiko 50,000: BahasaIndonesia Dansk Eesti Lietuvi Slovenina / Srpski Ting Vit
  • Hejuru y'inyandiko 20,000: Bahasa Melayu / Brezhoneg Bosanski English (simple) Euskara Galego Hrvatski slenska Latina Ltzebuergesch . Norsk (nynorsk) Shqip
